trans-unit.source: Represents a reference to a field.
CodeFieldReferenceExpression can be used to represent a reference to a field.
trans-unit.target: CodeFieldReferenceExpression 可以用于表示对字段的引用。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.TargetObject%2A> property specifies the object that contains the field.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.TargetObject%2A>属性指定的对象，其中包含字段。</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.TargetObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.FieldName%2A> property specifies the name of the field to reference.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.FieldName%2A>属性指定要引用的字段的名称。</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.FieldName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression"></xref> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression"></xref> class using the specified target object and field name.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression"></xref>类使用指定的目标对象和字段名称。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the object that contains the field.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> ，该值指示包含字段的对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the field to reference.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置要引用的字段的名称。

trans-unit.source: A string containing the field name.
trans-unit.target: 包含字段名称的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the object that contains the field to reference.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置包含要引用的字段的对象。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the object that contains the field to reference.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> ，该值指示包含要引用的字段的对象。
